{"tid":1387844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔啱聽都要講句！依家係仇恨憤怒主導緊你哋！","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:44:16.000Z","uid":77355,"like":98,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c1f117056882397476babc3363bf0ea4d3348c","tid":1387844,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:17:08.000Z","msg":"知道大家依家都好嬲 ，但係都唔好俾憤怒同仇恨主導緊你哋 ，越嚟越見到就算大家喺平日 冇裝備 沖曬上去 咁樣做同送頭有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n 我認為 大家 喺呢個時候 要冷靜自己情緒 唔好再畀仇恨同憤怒 去埋沒你嘅理知。 如果一味 用你嘅憤怒同仇恨 做任何決定 ，我覺得你可能就中咗班狗嘅計啦！<br />\n 有計劃有計謀去進行一個行動佢嘅成效好過你一味靠冲 之前有45位手足畀人捉咗 我唔想 再有多45個 我希望大家可以沉澱落嚟！<br />\n我都上過前線食個蛋， 但好多時候我哋都唔知為咗啲咩去守？<br />\n所以我想大家冷靜落嚟 諗下次行動 有咩計仔 講好咗要走一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d40930e81553f3fb4c4f1fd830dbacfafa04ad","tid":1387844,"uid":77355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"唔係叫你哋唔好冲，係要計劃過再冲"},{"pid":"f0a3c99df4bbda70ad1cda6620ee01611e18a2b6","tid":1387844,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bea200e2e8e58ae86c31b6f974b3dd113f0ecf","tid":1387844,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"頭先嗰個靚仔一個人想衝去揸長槍嘅白衫度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只可以係咁拉佢走 大家已經嬲到痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7932c44030fcf208d90f6456634a3c2c6ce4c40","tid":1387844,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:22:15.